ht: bold;&quot;&gt;Payment in Euro Currency&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;All payments will be made in Euro €.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Final price for reference is the price paid giving on your invoice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Where is the Wine Coming From?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px;&quot;&gt;We do not own the stocks. Your product will be shipped directly from the wineries to our warehouse, along with the necessary documentations. This process takes around 1 week (depending on the stock availability).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We collect and regroup in our warehouse all the products you will have ordered with precaution (collecting, grouping, filming &amp;amp; documents handling for exportation). This process takes 1 day when we confirm all your product are physically in our warehouse.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Handling &amp;amp; Shipping Service&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Shipping by sea process. &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;We clear customs on both sides&lt;/span&gt;, in France and Hong Kong and store the items in our warehouse in Hong Kong. This process may take around 24 to 40 days depending on the shipping liner company.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Delivery&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;We call you for delivery&lt;/span&gt;, don\'t worry and we\'ll organise everything with you. The appointment will be made to you before ship arrival so that we do not delay too much the delivery. Charges may apply if we have to return back the product and store them again in our warehouse. So be 